                <p>The hotel is an intimate venue designed by Wilmotte and located on rue du Conservatoire, a small street that is both away from the hustle of Paris and right in the heart of it. When I stay there, I can go to all my appointments by foot. And I love walking. During fashion week, if you are a bit claustrophobic, this is the great address.  And the restaurant La Régalade Conservatoire is excellent!</p>
