                <h2>2. Wallpaper Store - La Jeune Rue</h2>
                <p>La Jeune Rue is one of the projects demonstrating that Paris is still on the move ! It's very exciting. The combination of the best food and one of the most beautiful design projects has been a dream for Wallpaper for some time.  We will open our first Wallpaper shop in Paris here.</p>
